org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_AnalysisModel.SAM

Interface SaSharedResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, MutualExclusionResource, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SaSharedResourceImpl

    public interface SaSharedResource
extends MutualExclusionResource
    A representation of the model object 'Sa Shared Resource'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Capacity
    • Is Preemp
    • Is Consum
    • Acquis T
    • Release T
    See Also:
